%H A206453 <a href="/index/Rec#order_07">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (7,0,0,0,0,0,-1).
%F A206453 a(n) = 7*a(n-1) - a(n-7).
%F A206453 Empirical: a(n) = Sum_{i=0..floor(n/7)} ((-1)^i*7^(n-7*i)*binomial(n-6*i,i)).
%F A206453 G.f.: 1 / (1 - 7*x + x^7). - _Colin Barker_, Jun 16 2018
